# Code owners for ramflux.
#
# Review routing for pull requests. Security-, crypto-, and protocol-sensitive
# paths require review from a security maintainer (see GOVERNANCE.md and
# MAINTAINERS.md). Everything else falls back to the general maintainers.
#
# GitHub teams referenced here are maintained under the ramfluxhq org; the
# people behind them are listed in MAINTAINERS.md.

# Default: any change needs a maintainer review.
*                                   @ramfluxhq/maintainers

# Security-, crypto-, and protocol-sensitive paths: security maintainer required.
/crates/ramflux-crypto/            @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/crates/ramflux-protocol/          @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/crates/ramflux-node-core/         @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/crates/ramflux-transport/         @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/deny.toml                          @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/SECURITY.md                        @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/docs/threat-model.md               @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers

# CI / release / supply-chain surface: security maintainer required.
/.github/                           @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
/scripts/                           @ramfluxhq/security-maintainers
